<style src="./HomeView.css"></style>

<script>
// @ is an alias to /src

export default {
  name: 'HomeView',
  data() {
    return {
      areaName: "Главная"
    }
  },
  inject: ["areaList"],
  computed: {
      areasList() {
          let n_areaList = [];
          for (let i=2; i<this.areaList.length; i++) {
              n_areaList[i-2] = this.areaList[i]; 
          }
          return n_areaList;
      }
  },
}
</script>
